    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- WHAT IS DHI SECTION -->\n<section class=\"dhi-co-section\">\n  <div class=\"dhi-co-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n      <span class=\"mh-badge\">TECHNOLOGY</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">What is the DHI Method?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-description\">DHI (Direct Hair Implantation) is a modern hair transplant method that allows direct implantation of grafts without prior channel creation. Thanks to specialized instruments, the entire transplant process is very precise, gentle, and delivers natural-looking results.</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"dhi-explanation-grid\">\n      <div class=\"explanation-card\">\n        <div class=\"card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M18 2L22 6\"/><path d=\"M7.5 20.5L3.5 16.5L15 5L19 9L7.5 20.5Z\"/><path d=\"M15 5L19 9\"/><path d=\"M11 9L15 13\"/><path d=\"M7.5 20.5L2 22L3.5 16.5\"/><path d=\"M9 11L13 15\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Choi Implanter Pen</h3>\n        <p>A specialized instrument with a hollow needle into which a hair graft is inserted. This allows the doctor to implant the graft in one smooth step. It ensures precise placement of each hair.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"explanation-card\">\n        <div class=\"card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Direct implantation</h3>\n        <p>Grafts are implanted directly into the scalp without unnecessary waiting. This helps protect hair follicles, reduces tissue stress, and promotes faster healing.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"explanation-card\">\n        <div class=\"card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14H12L11 22L21 10H12L13 2Z\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>No channels needed</h3>\n        <p>Each hair graft is inserted individually, without prior channel creation. The DHI method allows precise control of the depth, direction, and angle of hair growth.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"dhi-placeholder dhi-image-wrap\">\n      <img src=\"https://maxhair.cz/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/choi-implanter-serena-cropped.png\" alt=\"Choi Implanter Pen - instrument for DHI transplantation\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"dhi-placeholder-img\" />\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"dhi-image-caption\">Photo of the specialized instrument used in the DHI method</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .dhi-co-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);\n    background: var(--white);\n  }\n\n  .dhi-co-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .section-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .dhi-co-section .section-header .mh-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 8px 24px;\n    background: var(--primary-gold) !important;\n    color: var(--black) !important;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    border-radius: 30px;\n  }\n\n  .section-title {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 20px 0;\n    letter-spacing: normal;\n  }\n\n  .section-description {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .dhi-explanation-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 32px;\n    margin-bottom: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .explanation-card {\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 40px 32px;\n    text-align: center;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .explanation-card:hover {\n    background: var(--white);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);\n    transform: translateY(-8px);\n  }\n\n  .card-icon {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    margin: 0 auto 24px;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  \n  .card-icon svg {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .explanation-card h3 {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  }\n\n  .explanation-card p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .dhi-placeholder.dhi-image-wrap {\n    padding: 0;\n    border: none;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    background: transparent;\n  }\n\n  .dhi-placeholder-img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    max-height: 400px;\n    vertical-align: top;\n  }\n\n  .dhi-image-caption {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 12px 0 0 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    background: transparent !important;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 1200px) {\n    .dhi-explanation-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .dhi-co-section {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .dhi-explanation-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 24px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
