    "id": "dhi_vyhody_code",
    "name": "code",
    "parent": "dhi_vyhody_container",
    "children": [],
    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- DHI BENEFITS SECTION -->\n<section class=\"dhi-vyhody-section\">\n  <div class=\"dhi-vyhody-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n      <span class=\"mh-badge\">BENEFITS</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Why choose the DHI Method?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-description\">Ideal for precision work and densification between existing hair</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"vyhody-grid\">\n      <div class=\"vyhoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"vyhoda-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M6 9V21H18V9\"/><path d=\"M6 9C6 7.89543 6.89543 7 8 7H16C17.1046 7 18 7.89543 18 9V9\"/><path d=\"M9 3V7\"/><path d=\"M15 3V7\"/><path d=\"M12 13V17\"/><path d=\"M10 11H14\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Suitable for fine hair</h3>\n        <p>The DHI method is ideal for fine hair and areas requiring maximum precision.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"vyhoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"vyhoda-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Precise placement</h3>\n        <p>The Choi Implanter Pen enables implantation of each graft with high precision following the natural hair growth direction.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"vyhoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"vyhoda-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 3V21H21\"/><path d=\"M7 16L12 11L15 14L21 8\"/><path d=\"M17 8H21V12\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Small to medium scope</h3>\n        <p>The DHI method is ideal for small to medium transplant areas.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"vyhoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"vyhoda-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 2L13.09 8.26L20 9L13.09 9.74L12 16L10.91 9.74L4 9L10.91 8.26L12 2Z\"/><path d=\"M19 19L20.09 21.26L23 22L20.09 22.74L19 25L17.91 22.74L15 22L17.91 21.26L19 19Z\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Densification between hair</h3>\n        <p>Ideal for densification between existing hair without the need to shave the head.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"vyhoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"vyhoda-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14H12L11 22L21 10H12L13 2Z\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Hairline design</h3>\n        <p>With maximum control over the angle and direction of hair growth, a completely new, precise, and natural hairline can be created.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"vyhoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"vyhoda-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"/><path d=\"M21 21L16.65 16.65\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Minimal scarring</h3>\n        <p>Thanks to micro-surgical instruments, only tiny micro-dots remain in the donor area, which are virtually invisible after healing.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .dhi-vyhody-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: clamp(50px, 6vw, 80px) clamp(20px, 4vw, 60px);\n    background: var(--white);\n  }\n\n  .dhi-vyhody-content {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .section-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);\n  }\n\n  .section-description {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 16px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    max-width: 700px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n\n  .vyhody-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 24px);\n    margin-top: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);\n  }\n\n  .vyhoda-card {\n    background: transparent;\n    padding: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 24px);\n    text-align: left;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);\n  }\n\n  .vyhoda-card:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none;\n  }\n\n  .vyhoda-icon {\n    width: clamp(24px, 3vw, 28px);\n    height: clamp(24px, 3vw, 28px);\n    margin-bottom: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 16px);\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n  }\n  \n  .vyhoda-icon svg {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .vyhoda-card h3 {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 18px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 clamp(8px, 1vw, 10px) 0;\n  }\n\n  .vyhoda-card p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.6vw, 14px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 992px) {\n    .vyhody-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .dhi-vyhody-section {\n      padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) clamp(20px, 3vw, 24px);\n    }\n\n    .vyhody-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
